These cakes are truly the gifts that keep on giving.  The covers can be adjusted from 8 lbs to 35 lbs.  It can be confusing when starting cloth diapering.  Giving a Taba Baby diaper cake helps take the confusion out of it.  Give that special someone in  your life the gift of cloth. name: Taba Baby Potty Training Cake
description:
As a mom, I know how difficult it can be to potty train.  This Cake is made to appeal to that little person in your life, ready for that next big step.

Contents include:

26 Pull-Ups size 2T-3T
Pull-Ups flushable wipes
Activity Pack
Blowers for success
A special toy

When beginning potty training, a lot of waiting is involved.  The activity pack and the special toy will keep your little guy or girl busy until it is time to GO.  When they finally make it to the potty for that first success, we have included party blowers to celebrate. 

Contact us for the reusable cloth training pants option.

This Special Cake would make for a wonderful second or third birthday party or just a wonderful marker for that next big step.

Comes in both boy and girl. 

Visit our Facebook page for more photos. Facebook.com/tabababydiapercakes

Can be made in any theme that will appeal to your special trainee, as well as the right size.
